\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{\{f(\frac{x}{2n})-f(\frac{x}{2n+1})\}}{\frac{x}{2n}-\frac{x}{2n+1}}\lt \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} M(\frac{x}{2n}-\frac{x}{2n+1})=M\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{x}{(2n)(2n+1)}
